    "form_header_text": "Congressman Nick Begich (AK-At large) FY27 Appropriations Request Form",
    "form_instructions_text": "Congressman Nick Begich invites you to submit requests for the FY27 Congressional appropriations cycle. The annual appropriations process allows Members to submit programmatic, language, and Community Project Funding requests to the Committee. Below is the form for programmatic and language requests, please DO NOT submit Community Projects Funding (CPF) requests on this form. Email James Lundquist, james.lundquist@mail.house.gov, for further information on CPF requests. Submitting a request for funding does not guarantee that funding will be submitted or appropriated. All requests must comply with House rules. Guidance and Deadlines will be updated once the House Appropriations Committee shares said information.",
