            "field_type": "text",
            "required": false,
            "options": null,
            "is_constituent_info": false,
            "is_prior_year_field": false,
            "draft_value": "Representatives Don Bacon (R-NE) and Judy Chu (D-CA)",
            "rationale": "Identifies the lead members of the existing House support letter mentioned in the reference values.",
            "confidence": "high"
          },
          {
            "field_id": "google_forms:01:entry_831687216:1f325238cd8d",
            "label": "State/Local Support:\n\nPlease indicate if there is a state or local government entity that is supporting this request, including if there are state or local government matching funds being allocated to support this request. ",
            "help_text": null,
            "field_type": "textarea",
            "required": false,
            "options": null,
            "is_constituent_info": false,
            "is_prior_year_field": false,
            "draft_value": "* University of Alaska Fairbanks (UAF), a state-funded institution, is the lead partner for critical NASA Science infrastructure in the district\n* UAF provides the institutional framework and facilities for the $34.8M synthetic aperture radar data archive and $14.2M domestic sounding rocket facility\n* While this is a federal account request, the efficacy of NASA Science funding relies on the continued partnership and infrastructure provided by the State of Alaska",
            "rationale": "UAF is the primary recipient in the district and a state institution. While there are no explicit 'matching funds' mentioned for the federal topline, the partnership with the state university is the local anchor for this request.",
            "confidence": "high"
          },
          {
            "field_id": "google_forms:01:entry_644321095:0f84d61647f0",
            "label": "Description of the Request:\n\nIf this is a language request, please limit the request to 2000 characters and include the exact language requested and whether this is bill or report language.\n\nIf this is a programmatic funding request, please limit the request to 500 characters and summarize the purpose of the request. ",
            "help_text": null,
            "field_type": "textarea",
            "required": false,
            "options": null,
            "is_constituent_info": false,
            "is_prior_year_field": false,
            "draft_value": "* $9 billion programmatic request for NASA's Science Mission Directorate (SMD)\n* Funding supports Earth Science, Planetary Science, Astrophysics, Heliophysics, and Biological and Physical Sciences\n* Sustains Decadal Survey priority missions to ensure U.S. global leadership in space discovery and innovation\n* Provides stability to the scientific workforce after significant budget disruptions in FY 2026",
            "rationale": "This captures the $9B ask and the programmatic nature of the request, highlighting the specific divisions and workforce stability as requested in the advocacy context.",
            "confidence": "high"
          },
          {
            "field_id": "google_forms:01:entry_548040323:8a436ce87fed",
            "label": "Relevance to Alaska:",
            "help_text": "Explain why this request is important to the state of Alaska.",
            "field_type": "textarea",
            "required": false,
            "options": null,
            "is_constituent_info": false,
            "is_prior_year_field": false,
            "draft_value": "* Directly impacts Alaska's economy with $62,606,127 in recent NASA Science obligations supporting high-skilled local jobs\n* Funds University of Alaska Fairbanks for the $34.8M synthetic aperture radar data archive and the $14.2M sounding rocket launch facility\n* Supports vital local research including community-driven freshwater ice monitoring and Arctic biodiversity data integration\n* Enables critical study of Alaskan permafrost and space plasma flows impacting Earth's atmosphere",
            "rationale": "Cites specific local spending data for AK-00, including the total obligations and the major contracts held by UAF for SAR data and sounding rockets.",
            "confidence": "high"
          },
          {
            "field_id": "google_forms:01:entry_1860349689:a27b46dee726",
            "label": "Any other information that you would like to include:",
            "help_text": null,
            "field_type": "textarea",
            "required": false,
            "options": null,
            "is_constituent_info": false,
            "is_prior_year_field": false,
            "draft_value": "* Space science is a strategic front in the race with China, which is aggressively expanding lunar and Martian ambitions to set 21st-century norms\n* NASA investments yield a 3-to-1 economic return, turbocharging the industrial and innovation workforce in the aerospace sector\n* Consistent funding prevents the loss of hard-won capabilities and prevents the displacement of civil servant and contractor expertise\n* Public polling consistently shows space science as a top priority for American citizens across bipartisan lines",
            "rationale": "Utilizes strategic advocacy talking points regarding international competition, economic ROI, and workforce stability to provide a broader justification for the $9B ask.",
            "confidence": "high"
          }
